'''Calibration Engineer''', along with [[Assembly Commander]], was one of the two most important positions on a [[World Devastator]]. The Calibration Engineer oversaw the [[molecular furnace]] and [[Force field/Legends|force fields]]. [[Deppo]] served as the ''[[Silencer-7]]''{{'s}} Calibration Engineer.

